139
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:43,920
Comment and follow people in your niche.

140
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,600
So, interact with posts.

141
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:48,959
And then after you've warmed up your account, download Cap Cut.

142
00:09:48,959 --> 00:09:50,000
It's super easy.

143
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:55,519
You can learn it in an hour and you can start posting videos from proven examples that you've seen.

144
00:09:55,519 --> 00:10:01,279
You spin them with your app either as a call to action at the end of the video, 3 seconds or less,

145
00:10:01,279 --> 00:10:03,040
