146
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:07,120
Make your caption and your first comment a call to action to go to your thing.

147
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:14,959
The algorithm loves watch time and the easiest way to get like 100% 200% watch time is to make your video 6 seconds long.

148
00:10:14,959 --> 00:10:18,880
